short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: It helps to import product reviews from AliExpress, Amazon, Etsy, Dhgate to TYH Platform.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You can import product reviews from AliExpress, Amazon to TYH Platform then show the reviews on your store.

Extension and App Features:
- Import Source: Aliexpress, Amazon, Etsy, DHgate
- Approve/Disapprove Reviews 
- Import Text Reviews and Photo Reviews
Support 2 platforms: Shopify, WooCommerce

Please contact us via our Live Chat or support tickers to get more information about our app or this extension.
